    <item>
      <title>股市在剧烈上涨后第二天遭抛售，波动性再度上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stocks-sell-off-a-day-after-furious-rally-as-volatility-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[原本希望度过一个平静夏天的投资者大失所望，因为动荡重创股市，在八月炎热天气到来之际，美国股票指数出现大幅波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stocks-sell-off-a-day-after-furious-rally-as-volatility-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:09:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MercadoLibre 利润较去年同期翻倍，超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/mercadolibre-meli-tops-estimates-with-profit-doubling-from-year-ago</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉丁美洲大型电子商务和支付公司 MercadoLibre Inc. 在第二季度的业绩超出了分析师的预期，同时其金融科技平台的用户数量创下了历史新高，表明其地域和产品扩张正在加速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/mercadolibre-meli-tops-estimates-with-profit-doubling-from-year-ago</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:08:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Carvana 首席执行官谈利润惊喜和债务削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/carvana-ceo-on-profit-surprise-and-debt-reduction-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Carvana 创始人兼首席执行官 Ernie Garcia 在“Bloomberg The Close”节目中讨论了公司的意外盈利和债务削减计划。Carvana 当期净利润为 4800 万美元，轻松超过分析师预期的近 1600 万美元亏损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/carvana-ceo-on-profit-surprise-and-debt-reduction-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:05:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Vertex 上调囊性纤维化药物收入预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/vertex-lifts-revenue-outlook-on-growth-of-cystic-fibrosis-drugs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Vertex Pharmaceuticals Inc. 上调了今年的销售预期，理由是其囊性纤维化药物的持续增长和镰状细胞病新疗法的推出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/vertex-lifts-revenue-outlook-on-growth-of-cystic-fibrosis-drugs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:04:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GitHub 开放 Copilot 模型访问权限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/github-opens-access-to-copilot-models-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[领先的人工智能开发者平台 GitHub 宣布扩展其人工智能战略，增加对其 Copilot 模型的访问权并对其进行新的扩展。GitHub 首席执行官 Thomas Dohmke 与 Ed Ludlow 一起讨论“彭博科技”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/github-opens-access-to-copilot-models-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:04:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南方电力称现有数据中心耗电量增加 17%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/existing-data-centers-suck-up-17-more-power-southern-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不仅仅是新建数据中心导致电力消耗大幅增加。首席财务官丹尼尔·塔克 (Daniel Tucker) 周四表示，南方公司辖区内现有数据中心第二季度的用电量与去年同期相比增加了 17%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/existing-data-centers-suck-up-17-more-power-southern-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 19:39:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员充分预期美联储今年将降息三次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bond-traders-are-fully-pricing-in-three-fed-rate-cuts-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府债券在经历了今年最好的月份之后，因经济数据而上涨，这些数据被视为巩固美联储今年三次降息的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bond-traders-are-fully-pricing-in-three-fed-rate-cuts-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 14:12:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
